hcc_text: East 163rd Street is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At East 163rd Street at Rev James Polite Avenue, Westchester Avenue and East 162nd Street, there were 2 deaths and severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
